#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Cbackend.md:18
msgid "Both workflows follow the same build process:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Cbackend.md:20
msgid ""
"1. Checkout code\n"
"2. Setup Node.js 20\n"
"3. npm ci                          (install all workspace dependencies)\n"
"4. Build shared package            (npm run build --workspace=@ronl/shared)\n"
"5. Lint backend                    (npm run lint in packages/backend)\n"
"6. Build TypeScript                (npm run build in packages/backend → "
"dist/)\n"
"7. Verify dist/index.js exists\n"
"8. Prepare deployment package:\n"
"     deploy/\n"
"       dist/                       (compiled TypeScript, structure preserved)"
"\n"
"       package.json                (backend package.json at deploy root)\n"
"       node_modules/@ronl/shared/  (shared package dist + package.json)\n"
"       node_modules/               (production dependencies only)\n"
"       .deployment                 (SCM_DO_BUILD_DURING_DEPLOYMENT=false)\n"
"9. Deploy to Azure Web App         (azure/webapps-deploy@v3, package: ./"
"packages/backend/deploy)\n"
"10. Wait 30 seconds\n"
"11. Health check with 5 retries (10-second intervals) → GET /v1/health\n"
"12. Verify /v1/health and /v1/dmns return HTTP 200"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Cbackend.md:41
msgid ""
"!!! warning \"Deployment package structure\" The `dist/` folder must be "
"copied as a folder (`cp -r dist deploy/`), not flattened (`cp -r dist/* "
"deploy/`). Flattening breaks TypeScript module resolution paths and causes "
"404 errors on all `/v1/*` endpoints after deployment."
msgstr ""

